# Platform Implementations

Each supported platform has its own implementation in the [media_platform/](mdc:media_platform/__init__.py) directory. Each platform module follows a similar structure:

## Common Structure
- `client.py` - API client for making platform requests
- `login.py` - Platform-specific login methods
- `core.py` - Core crawler implementation
- `field.py` - Enums and constants for the platform
- `help.py` - Helper functions

